<h3>Response Time</h3>
<p>I typically respond to emails within 24-48 hours. For urgent matters, Twitter DM might be faster.</p>
<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
<p><strong>Q: How often do you publish new content?</strong><br>
A: I aim for 1-2 high-quality posts per month. I prefer depth over frequency.</p>
<p><strong>Q: Do you accept guest posts?</strong><br>
A: Currently, I’m not accepting guest posts, but I’m always open to collaboration ideas.</p>
<p><strong>Q: Can I suggest topics for future articles?</strong><br>
A: Absolutely! Reach out with your suggestions - I love hearing what the community wants to learn about.</p>
<p><strong>Q: Do you offer consulting or freelance services?</strong><br>
A: I’m currently focused on my full-time role and this blog, so I’m not taking on freelance projects.</p>
<p><strong>Q: How can I stay updated with new posts?</strong><br>
A: You can follow me on social media or subscribe to the <a href="/feed.xml">RSS feed</a>.</p>
<hr>
<p><em>Thank you for reading and being part of the Tech Insights community! I hope you find the content helpful in your own development journey.</em></p>

